<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772093>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. Pronotum without (a, b, c) and with (d, e, f) marginal setiferous pores." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772093/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772095>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Labrum divided into three lobes (above: C. impressus) and two lobes (below: C. syrus)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772095/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772113>
    dc:description "Fig. 16. Batha (Mount Meron). Habitat of C. impressus, C. piochardi, C. syrus, and C. sidonius." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772113/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772115>
    dc:description "Fig. 17. Dune habitat (south of Ashdod). Habitat of C. impressus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772115/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772117>
    dc:description "Fig. 18. Steppe habitat (west of Be’er Sheva). Habitat of C. impressus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772117/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3770324>
    dc:description "Fig. 7. Aedeagus of C. impressus (a), C. syriacus (b), C. piochardi (c), C. syrus (d), C. lecordieri (e), C. sidonius (f), C. hemprichi (g), C. rumelicus (h), C. phoenix (i), and C. maurus (k)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3770324/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772099>
    dc:description "Fig. 8. Carabus impressus (Negev)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772099/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3770326>
    dc:description "Fig. 9. Carabus syriacus (Mount Meron)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3770326/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772119>
    dc:description "Fig. 19. Montane to subalpine pasture (Mount Hermon). Habitat of C. piochardi and C. rumelicus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772119/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772101>
    dc:description "Fig. 10. Carabus pio- chardi (Mount Meron)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772101/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3770318>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Elytron in lateral view, less rounded (above: C. syrus) and more rounded (below: C. sidonius)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3770318/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772097>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Mentum of Lamprostus species (a: C. syrus; b: C. lacordieri; c: C. sidonius)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772097/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772111>
    dc:description "Fig. 15. Quercus calliprinos dominated woodland (Ya’ar Bar’am). Habitat of C. impressus, C. piochardi, C. syrus, C. sidonius, and C. phoenix." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772111/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772103>
    dc:description "Fig. 11. Carabus syrus (Mount Meron)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772103/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772105>
    dc:description "Fig. 12. Carabus sidonius (Mount Meron)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772105/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3770320>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Last segment of maxillary palpi (a, b: C. rumelicus; c, d: C. maurus; a, c: male; b, d: female)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3770320/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772107>
    dc:description "Fig. 13. Carabus rumelicus (Mount Hermon)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772107/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3770322>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. Shoulder of elytron rounded (left: C. phoenix) and angulate (right: C. maurus)." ;
